People in their underwear and wrapped in blankets ran into the streets of Ya ' an and even the provincial capital of Chengdu , 115 kilometers east of Lushan , according to photos , video and accounts posted online . The quake ' s shallow depth , less than 13 kilometers , likely magnified the impact . Chengdu ' s airport shut down for about an hour before reopening , though many flights were canceled or delayed , and its railway station halted dozens of scheduled trains , state media said .